one.text: Equipping ladies with relevant Blockchain skills to thrive in the Web3 ecosystem
one.body: Our aim is to raise confident, audacious and technically sound Web3 ladies through our Web3 community and uniquely tailored mentorship cohorts.

two.body: We'll work hand in hand together, not only to challenge the status quo but also to create impactful open-sourced solutions as females in the Blockchain space.
